To generate a new miniconda for use on windows sytems:

1) Install the latest miniconda from https://repo.anaconda.com/miniconda/Miniconda3-latest-Windows-x86.exe - pick something like c:\mcstas-2.5\miniconda3 as install location

2) In a terminal, add the relevant paths for conda:
set PATH=c:\mcstas-2.5\miniconda3; c:\mcstas-2.5\miniconda3\Scripts;%PATH%

3) conda config --add channels conda-forge

4) conda install pyqt qscintilla2 pyqtgraph pyaml ply

5) Go to c:\mcstas-2.5 and create a zip file from the miniconda3 folder
